This paper is likely to belong to the Computational Linguistics (cs.CL) category as it deals with natural language processing and text analysis. The use of logistic regression and engineered features also suggests a focus on machine learning (cs.AI) and statistical learning (cs.LG). The paper also involves information retrieval (cs.IR) as it deals with the classification of news articles. Finally, the use of distant supervision and feature pre-processing suggests a potential focus on cybersecurity (cs.CY).
